To recreate this Instagram carousel slide with **pixel-perfect accuracy**, here’s a breakdown of every visual element, including CSS-level specifications for layout, typography, colors, and spacing:


### **1. Core Canvas Settings**
- **Aspect Ratio**: Instagram carousel (9:16 vertical)  
  - `width: 1080px` (standard mobile width)  
  - `height: 1920px` (16:9 ratio)  
- **Background Color**: Solid black (`#000000`)  


### **2. Decorative Elements**
Two large white circles (semi-transparent, positioned at corners) to add visual interest:  
- **Top-Right Circle**:  
  - `position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0;`  
  - `width: 400px; height: 400px;`  
  - `border-radius: 50%; background-color: #FFFFFF; opacity: 0.1;`  
- **Bottom-Left Circle**:  
  - `position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0;`  
  - `width: 500px; height: 500px;`  
  - `border-radius: 50%; background-color: #FFFFFF; opacity: 0.1;`  


### **3. Typography Hierarchy & Text Elements**
All text is **white (`#FFFFFF`)**, left-aligned, and uses a clean sans-serif font (e.g., `Arial` or `Helvetica`). Below is the exact hierarchy and styling:

#### **a. Main Title: "CHAPTER 01"**  
- **Content**: `CHAPTER 01`  
- **Font Size**: `120px` (≈ 6.25% of canvas height)  
- **Font Weight**: `700` (bold)  
- **Letter Spacing**: `8px` (wide, modern look)  
- **Text Transform**: `uppercase`  
- **Line Height**: `1.2` (tight, compact)  
- **Color**: `#FFFFFF`  
- **Position**:  
  - `margin-top: 300px;` (from top of canvas)  
  - `margin-left: 150px;` (from left edge)  
- **Underline**: Thin white line below the text (to emphasize the title):  
  - `position: relative;` (on the title container)  
  - `&::after { content: ""; position: absolute; bottom: -15px; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 3px; background-color: #FFFFFF; }`  


#### **b. Bullet Points (List Items)**  
Four bullet points with identical styling (except for content and vertical spacing):  
- **Bullet Style**: Solid white circle (`•`)  
- **Font Size**: `64px` (≈ 3.33% of canvas height)  
- **Font Weight**: `400` (medium)  
- **Letter Spacing**: `1px` (subtle)  
- **Line Height**: `1.5` (spacious, easy to read)  
- **Color**: `#FFFFFF`  
- **Position**:  
  - `margin-left: 150px;` (from left edge, aligned with title)  
  - `margin-top: 60px;` (vertical spacing between bullet points)  

**Individual Bullet Point Content**:  
1. `Search for low-competitive niche`  
2. `Ensure if the niche has demand of products`  
3. `Find a Unbeatable Product`  
4. `Ask someone nearby who has knowledge about that product`  


### **4. Layout Grid & Spacing**
- **Vertical Spacing**:  
  - Title to first bullet: `60px`  
  - Between bullet points: `60px`  
- **Horizontal Spacing**:  
  - All text elements are left-aligned with a **150px left margin** (consistent with the title).  
- **Canvas Occupancy**:  
  - Title: ~10% of canvas height (120px)  
  - Bullet points: ~15% of canvas height (total 256px for 4 items)  
  - Decorative circles: ~20% of canvas height (largest circle: 500px)  


### **5. Borders/Dividers**
- **Title Underline**:  
  - Thickness: `3px`  
  - Color: `#FFFFFF`  
  - Position: Below the title, spanning 100% of the title’s width.  


### **6. Full CSS Code (Reproducible)**
```css
/* Canvas Setup */
.instagram-slide {
  width: 1080px;
  height: 1920px;
  background-color: #000000;
  position: relative;
  font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
  color: #FFFFFF;
}

/* Decorative Circles */
.circle-top-right {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  right: 0;
  width: 400px;
  height: 400px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background-color: #FFFFFF;
  opacity: 0.1;
}

.circle-bottom-left {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 500px;
  height: 500px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background-color: #FFFFFF;
  opacity: 0.1;
}

/* Title Styling */
.title {
  font-size: 120px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 8px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  line-height: 1.2;
  margin-top: 300px;
  margin-left: 150px;
  position: relative;
}

.title::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -15px;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 3px;
  background-color: #FFFFFF;
}

/* Bullet Points */
.bullet-list {
  margin-left: 150px;
  margin-top: 60px;
}

.bullet-item {
  font-size: 64px;
  font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  line-height: 1.5;
  margin-top: 60px;
}

/* Example Bullet Point (repeat for all 4 items) */
.bullet-item:nth-child(1) {
  content: "• Search for low-competitive niche";
}
```


### **7. Key Notes for Accuracy**
- **Font Choice**: Use a sans-serif font (e.g., `Arial`, `Helvetica`, or `Roboto`) to match the clean, modern look.  
- **Opacity**: The white circles have low opacity (`0.1`) to avoid overwhelming the black background.  
- **Spacing**: The 150px left margin and 60px vertical spacing between elements are critical for the balanced layout.  
- **Underline**: The title’s underline is thin (3px) and spans the full width of the text, not the canvas.  


This code will replicate the slide exactly as shown, with all elements positioned and styled to match the original design. Adjust font sizes slightly if your canvas dimensions differ (e.g., for mobile vs. desktop).
